data.value:
We are pleased to enter into this agreement with you regarding the inclusion of your vehicle in the TooKCar car rental service. This agreement outlines the terms and conditions for rental of your vehicle through our platform. You agree to provide your vehicle, license plate number <Show Down> for rental purposes. The vehicle must be in good and roadworthy condition, with all necessary legal and insurance documents up to date.TooKCar will manage the advertisement, bookings, and rental operations for your vehicle. Your Payments will be transferred to your designated bank account on a monthly basis.
As the car owner, you are responsible for routine maintenance and ensuring the vehicle is insured at all times. Any damages caused during the rental period will be addressed through the customer’s insurance or as per TooKCar’s rental terms. This agreement will remain in effect from <Show Down> until terminated by either party with a written notice of <Show Down> Upon termination, all pending payments will be cleared, and the vehicle must be removed from the TooKCar platform. We look forward to a successful partership. If you have any questions require further clarification, please do not hesitate to contact
